Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.98,0:00:04.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}命运也是推理的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.69,0:00:06.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}神秘的事件也能看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k218}三只可爱的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.52,0:00:09.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}四个奇怪的养狗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.23,0:00:11.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k171}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.68,0:00:13.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k145}外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}Something's just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在找寻着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.46,0:00:26.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经习惯了谎言 现在也是一样 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.45,0:00:32.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有能够确定的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.22,0:00:41.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使一个人也不能哭泣 软弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.55,0:00:51.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}与真实的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在 映射出来 朝着两个人所决定的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝着没有尽头的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那里有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.51,0:01:18.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Oh yeah. You're going nowhere. It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}切实地前行着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.77,0:01:28.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}感受现在 you're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.77,0:01:47.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}无法消灭的证据（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.33,0:01:55.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是一只公的柴犬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.06,0:01:57.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}这只狗叫什么名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.19,0:01:59.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}它叫亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}这是取自创造出名侦探福尔摩斯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.16,0:02:04.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}亚瑟·柯南道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那它只要跟柯南联合起来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}就可以组成世界第一的侦探事务所了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.79,0:02:13.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}拜托 要我跟狗一起办案啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}你就不要挑剔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.47,0:02:16.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k119}女生的想象力肯定比较丰富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你不要奢求了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.87,0:02:19.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.63,0:02:24.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}十年后旧地重游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.32,0:02:25.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}这里还真变了不少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k254}你这么快就找到那个新盖的停车场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}那附近的道路比较复杂 不是很好找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}还好有小哀帮我看地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}我们才没有迷路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}亚瑟 不要再叫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.43,0:02:46.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k77}我从来没看过它这么激动过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}对别人大吼大叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}喂 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.35,0:02:55.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}你该不会在来之前摸过什么狗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.17,0:02:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且还是只比这只柴犬更大的公狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.70,0:03:04.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天早上一个朋友带了一只杜伯曼犬来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我跟小哀都摸了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}不过你是怎么知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}因为博士的衣服上面沾了些狗毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}狗光闻气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k115}就能辨识这只狗的体型和性别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.71,0:03:15.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k286}它们既然都是公狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.89,0:03:17.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}又知道对方比自己的体型大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}很自然就会产生敌意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.50,0:03:24.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k285}再加上博士和灰原刚才听了加纳先生的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才去把车子停到停车场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:31.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以亚瑟才会误以为博士和灰原你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}是被自己的主人赶跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}现在却又跑来找碴的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k238}这也难怪它会对你们大吼大叫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.34,0:03:40.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k133}你怎么那么白痴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}不过小地方不灵光这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}跟柯南搞不好还有点像哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.50,0:03:53.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它会这样误会完全是因为狗的习性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被朋友排挤的危险人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.64,0:04:02.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k286}这样诠释 其实对我来说也再恰当不过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 灰原…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}难道不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}光彦 我跟你说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}除了这点之外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.23,0:04:16.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}亚瑟之所以会狂吠还有另外一个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.20,0:04:23.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是你刚才制止亚瑟的声音实在太不果断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.39,0:04:25.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}狗该骂的时候就应该凶一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.75,0:04:26.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}要不然的话狗会以为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.05,0:04:31.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k131}主人是在为自己的这个举动加油打气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以后要多注意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}这位是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}他是我在爱犬协会里面认识的纲岛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他今天到这里来的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k137}刚好跟博士你们是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.38,0:04:47.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}这架飞机我先要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}我也是 我要这个娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}这样的话 那我就拿这个古老的沙漏好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.78,0:04:58.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这怎么好意思呢 这些东西价值不菲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:04:59.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k71}我过世的爷爷每次到国外旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}就会买些东西当做收藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k278}可是我跟爸妈对于古董又没有什么兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}卖掉对爷爷又有点说不过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.67,0:05:13.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}家父跟家母认为割爱给认识的朋友不算过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.34,0:05:17.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说到这里 怎么还没有见到他们两位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.57,0:05:22.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我爸妈昨天到刚盖好的新家去做搬迁的准备 所以不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.08,0:05:26.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而我呢 因为工作的关系必须长期住在英国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他们为了能够清静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.81,0:05:30.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k141}才决定搬到我乡下的叔叔家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以这栋房子的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}都必须要尽快地处理掉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实我这次会带去英国的只有亚瑟而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至于我爸妈要带的东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}也只有家母最爱的这只名叫道尔的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是蝴蝶犬嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k163}既然有了亚瑟跟道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}应该还有一只叫柯南的狗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k223}家父养过只牧羊犬名字就叫做柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}不过在两年以前它就已经病死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}不过不用担心 我们还有个柯南啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}步美 你把我当成狗啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}不过蝴蝶犬这个名字好奇怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.25,0:06:14.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实蝴蝶犬在法语就是蝴蝶的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.37,0:06:18.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是在16世纪的法国宫廷里最受欢迎的品种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}据说当时玛丽皇后的那只爱犬就是蝴蝶犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过它这身毛啊长得真是不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然不愧是得到大奖的好狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}大奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}家母曾经让它参加过一个比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}你可别小看它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.86,0:06:41.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}当时还有人愿意出一百万请她割爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.60,0:06:42.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一百万啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}大家都说这只狗既优雅又气派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}它又任性又爱撒娇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}这跟最后被送上断头台的那个法国皇后太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}土佐林小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}我是看你们的大门没关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}就没按门铃自己进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}我会来可是冲着你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k182}你要送我你母亲最爱的东西喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k254}那我就直说好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}客厅里除了那个大花瓶外 我都没有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}你们大家可以自己选你们喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k275}我就随便看看自己喜欢什么就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.21,0:07:17.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这位小姐也是爱犬协会的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实她以前的个性不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还不是从她的狗在比赛里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}输给道尔以后就开始生它的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}时候不早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k109}我早就看上和室那个挂钟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.11,0:07:33.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}不快点的话就要被那个女人抢走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.35,0:07:35.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}早知道 我就现在那个挂钟上贴上条子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}灰原同学你也拿点什么东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}这么难得的机会你也拿一样东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.84,0:07:44.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k259}这里有好多好好玩的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.97,0:07:46.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}既然这样我就要这只狗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果我像玛丽皇后一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k215}幻化为断头台上的雾水的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}那它是不是也会像它的爱犬提斯比一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.98,0:08:03.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k228}追随我的脚步 投身塞纳河之中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}真是个奇怪的女孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我说新一啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}你就让她打起精神来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.32,0:08:20.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}从那次公车事件以后她就一直不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}我就是看她老是窝在家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k162}才会带她来这里的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.76,0:08:25.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k285}怎么会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.22,0:08:30.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}那次事件后 公车上的乘客全都到警局接受笔录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.63,0:08:34.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是最后 也没查出哪个人身份可疑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.89,0:08:36.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也叫她不要担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}可是我看她这一次是真的很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}都没怎么好好地吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}晚上好像也睡不安稳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.12,0:08:49.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}无论如何 我只能肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}就算当时那些黑衣人真的也在那辆车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那也纯粹只是个巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}他们根本就没有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}灰原这个背叛者也会在公车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要不然 那件案子都已经过了十天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}他们早就把我们解决掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样你跟他们也逃不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我就说很奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.95,0:09:11.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k193}有道理哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.27,0:09:14.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}拜托 又在说什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}要是有你喜欢的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k113}你可千万不要客气哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}这样啊 那么 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}那我就拿这套音响好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}音响已经有人先预定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}亚瑟 你这样怎么行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}脚这么脏你怎么进屋来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.81,0:09:42.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}干什么啊 亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k215}好 我跟你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}我知道了 你放开我 亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到底是什么事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}我刚才已经按了好几次门铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}不过它好像坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}还好是亚瑟注意到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}才去帮我把你找来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.74,0:10:03.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}所以 请你千万别生它的气哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}不会 是我自己没有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}来 快去跟亚瑟玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它们感情好好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}那只狗是古英国牧羊犬 对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}对 它叫做克丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.75,0:10:24.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}原来它们是推理小说界的国王跟皇后啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}预定这套音响的 就是这位小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.37,0:10:32.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是想拿这套音响 庆祝我弟弟考上高中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.93,0:10:34.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是不关我的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k123}不过你还是快把它们分开比较好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.63,0:10:39.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它们要是有了孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k104}杂种狗可卖不到好价钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k272}你未免操太多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.45,0:10:48.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}反正亚瑟再过不久就要搬到英国去住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对吧 加纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔到底是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}这是它吃点心的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实我爷爷生前也很喜欢狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}所以我母亲 为了让我爷爷在过世之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}还能够看到道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:13.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}才会可以在和室的祭桌前面喂它吃点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 过不了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}这就变成了道尔的习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}往后和室的时钟 每次只要在12点响起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.65,0:11:22.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它就会先跑到和室里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k159}坐在垫子的上面静静地等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}坐垫子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}是啊 道尔最喜欢坐蓝色的坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它都会自动地咬垫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}到祭桌的前面坐下来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.51,0:11:39.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}可是到了半夜12点时钟不是也会敲响吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要是道尔弄错了又来等的话怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.77,0:11:43.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这点不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k149}我们找过钟表师傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}让那个时钟只有在中午12点的时候才会响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.45,0:11:53.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k139}我把这么重要的钟拿走的话不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实是我母亲说 我们不应该再宠它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}以后每天只要早晚喂它吃两顿就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.37,0:12:02.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}你们先从门缝里面看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔已经在里面了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}而且就坐在蓝色的垫子上面对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}没有看到道尔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}连蓝色的垫子都没有拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是不是因为蓝色的坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}跟咖啡色的坐垫叠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}它才没有办法拿出来坐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.67,0:12:27.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k71}其实它平常 就算垫子叠着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.56,0:12:30.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k189}它还是会用嘴把蓝色垫子抽出来再坐上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是怪了 它会跑哪去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}既然这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}那我们就分开来找好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}要是它跑到哪个角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k126}没办法动弹的话那就糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.31,0:12:40.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k126}道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}你在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k219}快点出来 道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}到处都没看到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.56,0:12:54.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}找到没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.92,0:12:55.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}没 没有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k121}我们连浴室里都找遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是亚瑟的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}还有克丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}竟然也跟着一起叫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}它们在后院 我们去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}焚化炉里竟然在冒烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}怎么会这样呢 那个焚化炉我们很早以前就没有在使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.99,0:13:23.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道说 不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.04,0:13:36.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是项圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}那…该不会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k243}道尔的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}不会的…不可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.81,0:14:02.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔…道尔…道尔…道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}别急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被烧掉的只有这个项圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.55,0:14:11.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}这个焚化炉里面并没有狗的骨骸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}话说回来 这真的是道尔的项圈吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k275}刚才没有看它戴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.19,0:14:19.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}平时项圈被毛遮住不容易看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然被烧焦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k93}不过我认得这个颜色和样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k221}因为这条项圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}是我爷爷过去为了以前养的那只蝴蝶犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}特地从法国买回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}一条古董狗项圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k147}你们来这边一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}后门的门锁被打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.76,0:14:38.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k116}这就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}这么说来绑走道尔的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.92,0:14:43.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}早就已经从后门逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 我不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}他干嘛把项圈丢进焚化炉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要把项圈拿掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}道尔就跟别的蝴蝶犬没有区别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}这条项圈上的装饰品实在是太醒目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 我倒不这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}因为犯人抓了狗之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k159}尽快逃离现场都来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.79,0:15:06.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}是不可能刻意把一个平常看不到的项圈丢进焚化炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.23,0:15:09.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还让别人知道他是从什么地方逃走的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人只是想故布疑阵 让人以为他已经逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那道尔就还在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.90,0:15:16.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k178}对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.85,0:15:20.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k95}这么一来 他把道尔藏在屋里某个地方的可能性就很高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.01,0:15:23.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 那这么说来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k228}博士 那个犯人该不会还在这个屋子里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.38,0:15:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂喂 你这话的意思该不会是在怀疑我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.34,0:15:37.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}不过 如果真的像这个小弟弟说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}那犯人是谁就很明显了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}因为 你们自己看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}那是一双女式皮鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}这是我的鞋 怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}你就少再装了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.96,0:15:52.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}这双鞋不正是你从玄关那里拿过来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.94,0:15:53.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}我没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k138}我想不可能啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k173}她如果是犯人的话 不可能把鞋子丢在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.84,0:16:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k278}再说如果她拿着鞋子 在屋子里面走动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}一定会有人注意到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k267}莲木小姐 你到这栋房子里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}也不是一次两次的事了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k221}既然这样 只要训练克丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}把鞋子从玄关拿到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}再让它回到玄关那里就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}这根本就不是一件什么困难的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}这怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}总而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}我们还是再去找一次道尔比较重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.43,0:16:30.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们几个小朋友就跟大哥哥一起去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.56,0:16:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}博士 你就跟他们三个一起找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过柯南啊 你说要找哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}刚才 我们都已经在屋子里找过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}很简单 这次找的不是狗可能躲的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而是人可能用来藏狗的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 我们让亚瑟也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.42,0:16:59.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k119}可以利用它的鼻子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k153}你应该没有忘记 鼻子是狗最厉害的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}狗的鼻子要比人的鼻子灵敏几百倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.03,0:17:11.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要让亚瑟先闻闻属于道尔身上的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它就应该会帮我们找到道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好了 我拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}这是道尔平常睡觉垫的垫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}来 亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}不过 它又不是受过训练的警犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.78,0:17:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 说不定这个方法真的会奏效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.42,0:17:32.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我父亲以前为了好玩 也常让亚瑟做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它好像知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}亚瑟到和室去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}那道尔一定在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蓝色的坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.05,0:17:50.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}这也对啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}道尔平常最喜欢的 就是蓝色的坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.75,0:17:56.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}狗怎么会喜欢蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.53,0:18:00.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}刚才我看的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k159}和室里明明只有两张蓝色坐垫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.61,0:18:08.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}加上亚瑟那张的话是三张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}竟然多了一张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.48,0:18:20.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样好像还是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}亚瑟有把鞋子藏起来的恶作剧的例子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有 事情正好相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}我记得亚瑟还是小狗的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k282}我每次只要一站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k109}它就会以为我要带它出去散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k201}就先跑到玄关那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}从鞋柜里面 把我的鞋子叼出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}乖乖地在那里等着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过等它知道我站起来不一定会带它散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.88,0:18:45.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k254}才没有再这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.44,0:18:47.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}这么厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k126}我就知道亚瑟不是一只普通的柴犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.16,0:18:54.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}来 再闻一次道尔的味道试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.81,0:18:59.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它好像知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.06,0:19:04.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}奇怪 它怎么停在客厅前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}它好像正在想什么事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它又往前走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}它往玄关那边走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}它到外面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}那个人一定是把道尔带到外面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.21,0:19:24.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k69}它根本是出来找克丽丝亲热的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}我想它一定是找烦了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}这就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.15,0:19:36.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}道尔生气的时候通常都会躲到什么地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我只是在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k104}那个犯人用蛮力把项圈拆掉的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.99,0:19:44.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k267}道尔会不会因为害怕 就自己躲到什么地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果是亚瑟害怕的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k103}它都会躲在我的床底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}躲在床底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.97,0:19:51.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k139}对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k121}因为刚养道尔的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}我们经常会对亚瑟发脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们只要在客厅里面逗弄还是小狗的道尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}亚瑟就会吃醋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}把客厅里面的坐垫咬破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过 它们现在相处得不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.88,0:20:13.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是要是道尔真的躲在哪里发抖 就太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.07,0:20:14.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}那种活在随时都有可能被发现的恐惧中的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的确是不太好受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}喂 你在搞什么啊 发什么神经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.27,0:20:25.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k115}我只是在对毫无对策的乐天派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.73,0:20:31.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}告知目前的状况有多么危险罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然我也不知道怎么会有这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k225}但是我可以肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}他们的人就在那辆公车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}要是那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.54,0:20:42.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k105}有任何事让他们注意到我的身份的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.74,0:20:44.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不只是我和你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k147}大家都会完蛋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}你就放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.81,0:20:51.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}我可以很肯定你的身份没有暴光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k282}为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k101}你为什么能说得这么肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}如果说你能够凭着嗅觉嗅出他们的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.83,0:20:59.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}我又何尝不能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}任何人身上只要带有杀气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.21,0:21:04.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}做侦探的都感觉得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}只是要知道杀气是谁发出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}就得费心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k228}我可以肯定那辆公车上没有这样的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当天根本就没有谁对你展现出明显的杀气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是什么表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.68,0:21:19.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k122}瞧不起侦探是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}不是瞧不起 是觉得你没救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.16,0:21:27.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k163}总之现在最重要的 是把事情再想过一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.60,0:21:31.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}道尔会不见还有哪些线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我记得道尔在听到中午12点的钟声敲响之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就立刻跑到和室吃点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}从此消失了踪影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}之后 我们所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.22,0:21:46.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}就跟在加纳先生后面到厨房去拿了奶酪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接着 到了和室才发现道尔不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后大家就分头在屋子的各个角落找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.92,0:21:57.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}按照屋子的平面图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.09,0:22:00.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}我们甚至连谁去找了哪里都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.31,0:22:04.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过犯人会把道尔藏在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.97,0:22:10.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还有他又打算怎样把道尔带离这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.46,0:22:47.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}会失去什么 即使现在开始 无所谓吧 能做得到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.55,0:22:58.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}尝试自己想做的事吧 直到与你相遇为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.71,0:23:04.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然什么都没有 闭上眼睛却能看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.94,0:23:09.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有个与你一起生活的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.78,0:23:16.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}always 将爱藏于胸口鼓起勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.33,0:23:20.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使失败也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.79,0:23:26.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}No 那并非所有的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.22,0:23:31.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Yes 趁风向转变的现在向前飞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.33,0:23:48.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下 我刚才看的时候明明是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.99,0:23:51.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个像棉花的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.91,0:23:53.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}好像是某种化学纤维
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.20,0:23:55.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}你要干嘛啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.69,0:23:59.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}道尔不会真的被丢到里面烧死了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.46,0:24:03.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此 原来犯人是用了那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.54,0:24:07.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是什么声音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.48,0:24:09.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}这是和室里的钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.12,0:24:12.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.54,0:24:14.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}无法消灭的证据（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.70,0:24:18.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.86,0:24:20.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}坐垫的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.93,0:24:21.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}道尔的假哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.36,0:24:22.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}亚瑟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.27,0:24:23.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k91}克丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.39,0:24:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k113}相同吗
